Subject: House Energy Committee Passes First Energy Package
Mime-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=us-ascii
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit
X-From: John Shelk <John Shelk/NA/Enron@ENRON>
X-To: Steven J Kean <Steven J Kean/NA/Enron@Enron>, Richard Shapiro <Richard Shapiro/NA/Enron@Enron>, James D Steffes <James D Steffes/NA/Enron@Enron>, Linda Robertson <Linda Robertson/NA/Enron@ENRON>, Christi L Nicolay <Christi L Nicolay/HOU/ECT@ECT>, Pat Shortridge <Pat Shortridge/Corp/Enron@Enron>, Tom Briggs <Tom Briggs/NA/Enron@Enron>, Chris Long <Chris Long/Corp/Enron@ENRON>, Sarah Novosel <Sarah Novosel/Corp/Enron@ENRON>, Ray Alvarez <Ray Alvarez/NA/Enron@ENRON>, Joe Hartsoe <Joe Hartsoe/Corp/Enron@ENRON>, Carin Nersesian <Carin Nersesian/NA/Enron@Enron>, Hap Boyd <Hap Boyd/EWC/Enron@Enron>, Lisa Jacobson <Lisa Jacobson/ENRON@enronXgate>, Jeffrey Keeler <Jeffrey Keeler/Corp/Enron@ENRON>
X-cc: 
